  <summary date="2021-04-07T20:12:55Z" status="Introduced in House">Vaccine Fairness Act

This bill requires the Department of Health and Human Services (HHS) to provide weekly reports to Congress concerning the distribution of COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) vaccines to the public.

HHS must also make publicly available certain data on the number of vaccine doses administered.</summary>
